<view class="page"><view class="title">经营报表</view><view class="subtitle">按当前企业租户统计保费、参保人员和理赔数据</view><view wx:if="{{loading}}" class="loading">正在生成报表…</view><view wx:for="{{items}}" wx:key="id" class="card section"><view class="row between"><text class="list-title">{{item.name}}</text><text class="tag">{{item.period}}</text></view><view class="amount" style="margin-top:24rpx">{{item.value_text}}</view><view class="list-meta">{{item.detail}}</view></view><view class="card notice"><view class="strong">统计口径</view><view class="list-meta">按月方案根据当月实际保障天数折算；按天方案按日费率与保障天数计算。</view></view></view>
